name: Unidentified_Twi%27lek_(Buck_Vancto)
content: A Twi'lek individual lived during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 8 BBY and 2 BBY, the Twi'lek provided Marshal Buck Vancto with a job to capture the Snivvian criminal Brox Anthar, who was wanted for multiple acts of grand larceny. Whilst Vancto was carrying out the job, the Twi'lek contacted Vancto and informed the marshal of a new job assigned to them. As the Twi'lek provided background details on the marshals target, they sent over a holo of him, the smuggler Han Solo.
